## Limitations

The report is based on publicly available opinions and case studies, which may not cover all aspects of the issue comprehensively. The data is also limited to the perspectives and contexts provided by the sources, which may not be universally applicable. Additionally, the financial and logistical specifics of implementing free public transport can vary significantly by region, which is not fully explored in this report.

